{"tid":2113080,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[三分鐘學整] 蝦醬蒸腩肉","createTime":"2020-07-18T00:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T03:30:50.000Z","uid":333435,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21741992b3a0ddbda7486c1234247c5d73bc7929","tid":2113080,"uid":333435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"尋日好柒咁post錯區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日係依度post番<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣好鐘意蝦醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一食就停唔倒口<br />\n雖然大肚唔可以食太多濃味野，但蒸完出黎真係忍唔住要食多兩舊！<br />\n夾埋腩肉嘅油香，真係抵抗唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係屋企都想整黎食嘅你，快d㩒入去睇下詳細做法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0CtNwxbrzXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0CtNwxbrzXo&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=6f77889f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0CtNwxbrzXo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5fh1rE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5fh1rE.jpg&h=2de9c89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴絲打支持！鐘意我地教學嘅可以俾個like同subscribe 我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&amp;nbsp;有咩想學都可以留言講啊！<br />\n<br />\n上回教學：<br />\n芫荽豆腐湯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2109830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2109830</a><br />\n<br />\n蒸水蛋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2106706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2106706</a><br />\n<br />\n芋頭椰汁西米露<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2102527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2102527</a><br />\n<br />\n港式麻婆豆腐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2099729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2099729</a><br />\n<br />\n日式咖哩雞肉飯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2097001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2097001</a><br />\n<br />\n日式照燒三文魚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094311</a><br />\n<br />\n梅菜扣肉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2092869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2092869</a>"},{"pid":"1af79698b75669a3f3560ffbcdcd910d29abca7c","tid":2113080,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193d3691e028a1c93b500ca6331c6873b3e59d9d","tid":2113080,"uid":333435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af79698b75669a3f3560ffbcdcd910d29abca7c","tid":2113080,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"又俾你捉倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f29d1d1c3bca69d9cae4e36aa18c9f5528efb17","tid":2113080,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"193d3691e028a1c93b500ca6331c6873b3e59d9d","tid":2113080,"uid":333435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af79698b75669a3f3560ffbcdcd910d29abca7c","tid":2113080,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/